{"tid":2229260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"靠檢測棄口罩 防疫失敗","createTime":"2020-10-04T08:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T09:28:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd681b265711c79e341363823fae0812cb301d2","tid":2229260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/DX52LWZKGVGFPKJQPKU6TS3QF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FDX52LWZKGVGFPKJQPKU6TS3QF4%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=af68d9d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FDX52LWZKGVGFPKJQPKU6TS3QF4%2F&h=c27ab490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/DX52LWZKGVGFPKJQPKU6TS3QF4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n靠檢測棄口罩 防疫失敗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qfp6bzsPRJQMdOMgHBqRC9v9w6U=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3EKR57KK5ZDUJGWJNCQFVE44EE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQfp6bzsPRJQMdOMgHBqRC9v9w6U%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3EKR57KK5ZDUJGWJNCQFVE44EE.jpg&h=1a61c8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■白宮提名儀式出席者對防疫掉以輕心，不少人未有保持社交距離。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n自武漢肺炎爆發以來，特朗普多次淡化戴口罩和保持社交距離的抗疫效用，主要依靠為身邊人員進行病毒測試防疫。如今他與多名身邊人一同染病，證明僅以檢測防疫並非可靠方法。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：白宮醫生稱特朗普退燒  知情者指淡化病情 未來48小時關鍵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n室內狹窄環境聚集易播毒<br />\n<br />\n特朗普近月多次出席公開活動時，都被拍攝到沒有戴口罩，又公開表示不應強制戴口罩和應盡快放寬社交距離限制，違反抗疫專家的建議。即使在白宮內，職員都甚少跟從指引戴口罩，並經常在狹窄的室內環境聚集，外界早已擔心白宮會成為播毒溫床。<br />\n<br />\n令特朗普和一眾白宮人員在疫症下敢於不設防的，相信是當局採用的快速測試系統。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：提名儀式爆群組 華府淪陷  七出席者確診 恐毒襲辯論會<br />\n<br />\n美國範德堡大學傳染病學教授沙夫納（William Schaffner）表示，。。。。。。。。。。。。，形容特朗普在玩火，認為如他有戴口罩，就有機會避免被身邊人傳染。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"30f61fad47e6e86628e892bc3f216a22b93403e2","tid":2229260,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"侵侵唔會有事<br />\n波仔嗰陣都話入icu啦<br />\n而家咪又係乜事都無"},{"pid":"b4d71b98ac0f05fa81f9a16102f919ea954f4482","tid":2229260,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"其實係生產唔夠咁多口罩，冇辦法"}]}